<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idab49b135-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s8753"><num value="8753">§ 8753.</num><heading> Tolls and fares: payment or reimbursement</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Naval appropriations chargeable for transportation or travel are available for the payment or reimbursement of ferry, bridge, and similar tolls and of streetcar, bus, and similar fares.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idab49b136-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/464">70A Stat. 464</ref>, § 7523; renumbered § 8753, <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s807/d/7">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 807(d)(7)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1836">132 Stat. 1836</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
